    <section class="section-container" id="shop">
        <h2 class="hollow-heading">The Avyen Two-Step Hair Ritual</h2>
        <p class="section-ritual-sub">A gentle cleanse followed by a soft, smooth finish — created for hair that feels clean, balanced, and effortlessly cared for.</p>
        <div class="products-grid">
            <a href="/products/scalp-cleanse" class="product-item">
                <div class="product-item-img">
                    <img src="{{ 'scalp-cleanse.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Avyen Scalp Cleanse">
                </div>
                <h3>Avyen Scalp Cleanse</h3>
                <p>A gentle, plant-based hair cleanser formulated to cleanse the scalp effectively while maintaining its natural balance.</p>
                <div class="price">Rs. 2,390</div>
