    <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="how-it-works-heading">
        <div class="how-it-works__inner">
            <h2 class="how-it-works__heading" id="how-it-works-heading">A Simple Ritual for Soft, Balanced Hair</h2>
            <div class="how-it-works__steps">
                <div class="how-step">
                    <div class="how-step__num">Step 1</div>
                    <h3 class="how-step__title">Cleanse</h3>
                    <p>Apply Avyen Scalp Cleanse to wet hair and scalp. Massage gently and leave for 1–2 minutes. Rinse thoroughly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="how-step">
                    <div class="how-step__num">Step 2</div>
                    <h3 class="how-step__title">Condition</h3>
                    <p>After shampooing, apply Avyen Conditioning Creme to clean, wet hair. Focus on mid-lengths and ends.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="how-step">
                    <div class="how-step__num">Step 3</div>
                    <h3 class="how-step__title">Soften &amp; Smooth</h3>
                    <p>Leave for 3–5 minutes, then rinse thoroughly for a soft, smooth, effortless finish.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="benefits-section" aria-labelledby="benefits-heading">
